    "description": "OIZUMI Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the manufacture and sale of automatic service equipment, system equipment, and gaming machines for entertainment industry in Japan. The company offers medal polishing, supplying and recovery system, medal and medal lending machine, and bill transport system, as well as pachislot and panchiko machines, and gaming machine mechanism units; ball supply and recovery systems; game center POS; and ball storage systems. It also provides maintenance, information processing, and real estate rental and management services; spart parts; game software; and package games, video/music, publishing, and online amusement. In addition, the company is involved in licensing of ball supplying machine related patents; development of amusement park information systems; and internet content distribution. Further, it operates solar power generation and other, as well as food and e-commerce businesses; generates and sells electricity; manufactures, processes, and sells agricultural products, such as jelly and jellies; and develops health foods and cosmetics. The company was incorporated in 1974 and is based in Atsugi, Japan."
